The paper explores the role of books in scholarly communication, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of the COCI dataset also involves computational methods (cs.CY) and data analysis (cs.SI). Additionally, the study may be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) as it involves analyzing a large dataset.
